title: O365 Saturday Canberra
eventShortDescription: ​O365 Saturday Events are free events held in most capital cities in Australia throughout the year.  At each event there are no less than 10 fantastic sessions covering all aspects of Office 365 presented by respected professionals in various fields.​ ​ ​ ​​
